description:
Danny and Whitney talk eBay scams and Southern Charm. Danny also welcomes celebrity chef & author Stuart O'Keeffe to break down #RHONY. PLUS, Dr. Amador (psychologist from #RHONY & Bethenny Ever After/founder of the LEAP Institute) calls in to talk mental health. 

*For bonus episodes, join the Patreon at www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic Web: www.EverythingIconic.com Twitter: www.Twitter.com/DannyPellegrino Instagram: www.Instagram.com/DannyPellegrino
